0Z","msg":"<blockquote>打奶有咩技術？<br />\n<br />\n個steam機好勁一兩秒已經六七十度<br />\n泡打得好粗 想學拉花唔係次次成功</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成套動作機器化<br />\n1放氣 2插steam入奶至覆蓋氣孔 3開steam 4即刻即刻即刻拉低奶缸打泡 5水位上升後hold一陣(呢個動作叫打綿)6推高奶缸，令奶泡同奶融合，直至辣手3秒左右熄steam<br />\n<br />\n重點，拉低奶缸入泡嗰陣唔好拉太低，啲聲會係支支支支聲，唔係支支支包支<br />\n<br />\n仲有，記得要快少少搵到個風眼，拉曬啲粗嘅奶泡落去"},{"pid":"096778ddf1afc09081d8766c068c3ca9b739f1f9","tid":395394,"uid":19872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T19:27:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做緊垃圾SB表示有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊區？</blockquote><br />\n綠色線<br />\n你間咖啡店係邊？ 想尼試下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b352d564c7c31840e9fa4151ecda121ddb10a5","tid":395394,"uid":112608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T21:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實好多人都做cafe<br />\n我自己都係<br />\n冇咩想問</blockquote><br />\n你做邊間？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小型咖啡店 並非連鎖<br />\n我地晏晏startup做起 (:"},{"pid":"05ca41c823ec4bd22151972310db044a3b2b5e43","tid":395394,"uid":133485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:15:10.000Z","msg":"有冇做埋烘焙"},{"pid":"4d92af2e97eb0661afe0a86389ab27abd2511336","tid":395394,"uid":56657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:27:45.000Z","msg":"人工最高可以去到幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最終會唔會自己開鋪？"},{"pid":"df83cecbed254e0eff7f8426cfe33ee908f111c7","tid":395394,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T03:32:49.000Z","msg":"我明天開始上堂（full time)1個月<br />\n咖啡沖調及相關飲品<br />\n<br />\n學完想出來實習<br />\n關照吓丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：5年後儲夠水腳想自己開"},{"pid":"9139481e7ed7d5e9a34405be4f224ec3a5a8a35a","tid":395394,"uid":87689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>lm 想做pt學沖咖啡</blockquote><br />\n邊區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留telegram</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n觀塘區 <br />\ntg： knowatree"},{"pid":"d65ca6ea3ba9d55b4a95a69ea8e3b55325661ca6","tid":395394,"uid":63164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做過垃圾starbucks，真心想做小型cafe。 但自己資歷好淺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ff0bb8bead4d0b9edb73ba18f33946c4b99e3a36","tid":395394,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"0經驗，係邊度學?. 點起手?"}]}